# Skill: Retro

Use `.ai/lifecycle/reflect.md` before closing the work.

Create `retro-YYYY-MM-DD.md` with:

- Notable PRs / features shipped
- Recurring review comments (a11y, perf, tests)
- Flaky tests or E2E pain
- Bundle size trend (if tracked)
- Action items → update `.ai/rules/` when patterns repeat
- Missing lifecycle, rule, skill, or adapter guidance discovered during delivery
- Follow-up tasks with owners or next actions
